name:                ivory
version:             0.1.0.2
author:              Galois, Inc.
maintainer:          trevor@galois.com
category:            Language
synopsis:            Safe embedded C programming.
description:         Using GHC type-system extensions, enforces safe low-level programming, while maintaining expressiveness.
